hnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.2621em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>求导：</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>z</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>z</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow></mfrac><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∂</mi><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>t</mi><mo separator=\"true\">⋅</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>y</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial x}=\\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial t}\\frac{\\partial t}{\\partial x}=2t·1=2(x+y)\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.0574em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3714em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">∂</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">∂</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.04398em;\">z</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.0574em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3714em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">∂</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">∂</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.04398em;\">z</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.3714em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">∂</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">∂</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">t</span><span class=\"mpunct\">⋅</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>反向传播计算图：</p>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240918143651688.png\" alt=\"image-20240918143651688\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<p><code v-pre>加法的反向传播</code>：将上游的值传给下游，并不需要正向传播的输入信号</p>\n<p><code v-pre>乘法的反向传播</code>：需要正向传播时的输入信号值。因此，实现乘法节点的反向传播时，要保存正向传播的输入信号</p>\n<p>苹果和橘子问题反向传播计算图：</p>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240918151307894.png\" alt=\"image-20240918151307894\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<h4 id=\"反向传播计算图\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#反向传播计算图\"><span>反向传播计算图</span></a></h4>\n<p><mark>反向传播的计算顺序</mark>：将节点的输入信号乘以节点的局部倒数（偏导数），然后再传递给下一个节点</p>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240918140438143.png\" alt=\"image-20240918140438143\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<h4 id=\"线性层的反向传播\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#线性层的反向传播\"><span>线性层的反向传播</span></a></h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>仿射变换：在几何中包括一次线性变换和一次平移，即加权和运算、加偏置运算</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>单数据Affine层计算图：</p>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240918204945600.png\" alt=\"image-20240918204945600\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<p>批版本Affine层计算图：</p>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240918210329672.png\" alt=\"image-20240918210329672\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<p>偏置在正向传播中使用广播机制加到<span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>∗</mo><mi>w</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x*w</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4653em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">∗</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02691em;\">w</span></span></span></span>中</p>\n<p>反向传播中各个数据的反向传播值要汇总为偏置的元素</p>\n<h4 id=\"激活函数层的反向传播\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#激活函数层的反向传播\"><span>激活函数层的反向传播</span></a></h4>\n<p><code v-pre>函数、计算图、导数</code></p>\n<h5 id=\"relu-1\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#relu-1\"><span>ReLU</span></a></h5>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">{</mo><mtable rowspacing=\"0.36em\" columnalign=\"left left\" columnspacing=\"1em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mi>x</mi></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mn>0</mn></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"false\"><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>⩽</mo><mn>0</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr></mtable></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">y=\\begin{cases}x&amp;(x&gt;0)\\\\0&amp;(x\\leqslant0)\\end{cases}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:3em;vertical-align:-1.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size4\">{</span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mtable\"><span class=\"col-align-l\"><span class=\"vlist-t vl