/span></a></h4>\n<h5 id=\"batch-normalization\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#batch-normalization\"><span>Batch Normalization</span></a></h5>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>(N, C, H, W)，在通道C上计算均值和标准差</strong>[:, 0, :, :]-&gt;[:, 1, :, :]-&gt;[:, 2, :, :]-&gt;[:, 3, :, :]-&gt;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>原始分布：卷积后数据可能偏向某一区域（如均值较大、方差较小）</li>\n<li>归一化：分布被调整为均值为0、方差为1的标准正态分布</li>\n<li>缩放和平移：通过调整 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>γ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\gamma</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">γ</span></span></span></span> 和 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>β</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\beta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05278em;\">β</span></span></span></span> 调整分布，稳定数据分布</li>\n</ul>\n<p>放置位置：卷积之后，激活函数之前</p>\n<p>注：实际推理过程中使用的 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>γ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\gamma</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">γ</span></span></span></span> 和 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>β</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\beta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05278em;\">β</span></span></span></span> 来自于训练得到</p>\n</blockquote>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241213164206788.png\" alt=\"image-20241213164206788\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<ol>\n<li>求每个训练批次数据的均值</li>\n<li>求每个训练批次数据的方差</li>\n<li>使用均值和方差对该批次数据标准化，得到0-1分布</li>\n<li>尺度变换和偏移：使用标准化之后的 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span> 乘以 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>γ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\gamma</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">γ</span></span></span></span> 调整数值大小，再加上 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>β</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\beta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05278em;\">β</span></span></span></span> 增加偏移后得到输出值 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">y</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span></span></span></span> 。【(训练参数)<span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>γ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\gamma</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">γ</span></span></span></span>：尺度因子；<span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>β</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\beta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05278em;\">β</span></span></span></span>：平移因子】</li>\n<li>由于标准化后的 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span></span></span></span> 基本会被限制在正态分布下，会使得网络的表达能力下降，为了解决这个问题，引入两个模型参数 <span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>γ</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\gamma</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05556em;\">γ</span></span></span></span> 、<span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>β</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\beta</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8889em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05278em;\">β</span></span></span></span> 进行平移变化</li>\n</ol>\n<p>实际使用时可能采用类似momentum动量法中使用的滑动平均来进行计算测试时候的均值和方差</p>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable rowspacing=\"0.25em\" columnalign=\"right left\" columnspacing=\"0em\"><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mi>E</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>B</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><msub><mi>μ</mi><mi>B</mi></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo></mrow></mstyle></mtd></mtr><mtr><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow></mrow></mstyle></mtd><mtd><mstyle scriptlevel=\"0\" displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow></mrow><mi>V</mi><mi>a</mi><mi>r</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">[</mo><mi>x</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">]</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>m</mi><mrow><mi>m</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>B</mi></ms