240918151307894\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<h4 id=\"反向传播计算图\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#反向传播计算图\"><span>反向传播计算图</span></a></h4>\n<p><mark>反向传播的计算顺序</mark>：将节点的输入信号乘以节点的局部倒数（偏导数），然后再传递给下一个节点</p>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240918140438143.png\" alt=\"image-20240918140438143\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<h4 id=\"线性层的反向传播\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#线性层的反向传播\"><span>线性层的反向传播</span></a></h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>仿射变换：在几何中包括一次线性变换和一次平移，即加权和运算、加偏置运算</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>单数据Affine层计算图：</p>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240918204945600.png\" alt=\"image-20240918204945600\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<p>批版本Affine层计算图：</p>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20240918210329672.png\" alt=\"image-20240918210329672\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<p>偏置在正向传播中使用广播机制加到<span v-pre class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>∗</mo><mi>w</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">x*w</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4653em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">∗</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.4306em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02691em;\">w</span></span></span></span>中</p>\n<p>反向传播中各个数据的反向传播值要汇总为偏置的元素</p>\n<h4 id=\"激活函数层的反向传播\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#激活函数层的反向传播\"><span>激活函数层的反向传播</span></a></h4>\n<p><code v-pre>函数、计算图、导数</code></p>\n<h5 id=\"relu-1\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#relu-1\"><span>ReLU</span></a></h5>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span 