zing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p><strong>总结</strong></p>\n<p>优点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>适用于图像风格化，依赖于每个图像实例</li>\n<li>不受样本批次大小的影响，保证每个feature map的独立性</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"group-normalization-layer\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#group-normalization-layer\"><span>Group Normalization Layer</span></a></h5>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>(N, C, H, W)，在每个样本的每组通道C/G上计算均值和标准差</strong>[:, group0, :, :]-&gt;[:, group1, :, :]-&gt;[:, group2, :, :]-&gt;[:, group3, :, :]-&gt;</p>\n<p>GN = LN + IN</p>\n</blockquote>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241213201631836.png\" alt=\"image-20241213201631836\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" />\n<p><strong>总结</strong></p>\n<p>优点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>针对于BN在小batchsize效果差的问题</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"归一化效果对比\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#归一化效果对比\"><span>归一化效果对比</span></a></h5>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241213201749628.png\" alt=\"image-20241213201749628\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241213201715303.png\" alt=\"image-20241213201715303\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n<h5 id=\"switchable-normalization-layer\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#switchable-normalization-layer\"><span>Switchable Normalization Layer</span></a></h5>\n<blockquote>\n<p>前三者的结合，提出自适配归一化方法，自动为神经网络中每个归一化曾确定合适的归一化操作</p>\n<p>SN = BN + IN + LN</p>\n</blockquote>\n<img src=\"@source/notes/read/深度学习-CV.assets/image-20241213201228993.png\" alt=\"image-20241213201228993\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" />\n$$\n\\hat{h}_{ncij}=\\gamma\\frac{h_{ncij}-\\Sigma_{k\\in\\Omega}w_k\\mu_k}{\\sqrt{\\Sigma_{k\\in\\Omega}w_k^{\\prime}\\sigma_k^2+\\epsilon}}+\\beta,\n$$\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" dis