mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">t</span><span class=\"mpunct mtight\">,</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\">i</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>优点：减少学习率的手动调整，更适用于稀疏数据，提高SGD的鲁棒性。</li>\n<li>缺点：分母会不断累积，学习率衰减越来越快。</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"rmsprop\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#rmsprop\"><span>RMSProp</span></a></h4>\n<blockquote>\n<p>为了解决 AdaGrad 学习率急剧下降</p>\n<p>是 Geoff Hinton 提出的一种自适应学习率方法。结合了Momentum的惯性原则，加上AdaGrad对错误方向的阻力。但是缺少了Momentum的一部分，因此后面Adam补上这个想法。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p v-pre class='katex-block'><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>β</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>v</mi><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>+</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>β</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><msubsup><mi>g</mi><mi>t</mi><mn>2</mn></msubsup><mspace linebreak=\"newline\"></mspace><msub><mi>θ</mi><mrow><mi>t</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi>η</mi><msqrt><mrow><msub><mi>v</mi><mi>t</mi></msub><mo>+</mo><mi>ϵ</mi></mrow></msqrt></mfrac><msub><mi>g</mi><mi>t</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">v_{t}=\\beta_{1}v_{t-1}+(1-\\beta_{1})g_{t}^{2}\\\\\\theta_{t+1}=\\theta_{t}-\\frac{\\eta}{\\sqrt{v_{t}+\\epsilon}}g_{t}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5806em;vertical-align:-0.15em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588